{"tid":1468516,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【絕不割席】每天修正缺失，先係致勝關鍵！","createTime":"2019-08-13T19:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:44.000Z","uid":282947,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ce372fbfcd4a014049882719d61f8e2e7693fe","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:01:41.000Z","msg":"我都知P牌仲要第一次出post實比人歧視，唔緊要，我講得唔啱即管負評我啦。<br />\n先講明，<span style=\"color: red;\">不割席、不分化。</span><br />\n大家所有野都係呢兩個月先學，一定有做得唔好嘅地方，我地一齊邊做邊修正啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日需承認嘅缺失：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">忘記左大家入機場係要喺國際鏡頭前，比全世界睇到我地係受害者。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n修正建議如下：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 唔好主動阻止旅客登機</span></strong><br />\n好多人靜坐，然後政府取消航班，旅客會覺得佢地反應誇張，連出嚟為女急救員聲討警暴都唔可以？<br />\n但如果係我地主動攔截旅客登機，加上政府取消航班，旅客就會覺得啱啊真係亂吖嘛。<br />\n點解我地要爭取旅客認同？<span style=\"color: red;\">因為旅客就係一個活生生嘅移動文宣，佢會將喺香港嘅見聞帶返外國！</span><br />\n要記住，癱瘓機場係我地嘅<strong>hidden agenda</strong>，牌面我地係做緊聲討警暴集會，所以我地嘅角色係要被動。<strong>哎唷，我地嚟坐下，政府都要取消航班，唔知係邊個搞著旅客呢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 做好外語文宣，熱心服務旅客</span></strong><br />\n大家係黎機場表達香港市民係受害者，唔該唔好淨係坐喺度篤手機、傾計啦。口號都唔好淨係叫中文啦。<br />\n<strong>你地target audience係外國鏡頭同遊客啊！！！</strong><br />\n最好高舉一啲寫住「I can speak in English. Do you need help?」嘅牌，等遊客主動approach你，<span style=\"color: red;\">你一邊帶路，一邊置入式宣傳香港發生咩事，效果點都比你淨係叫口號強。</span><br />\n再講多次，旅客喺香港經歷啲咩，返家鄉就係最好嘅人肉文宣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而香港之前嘅遊行咁令佢地impressive，就係因為香港人嘅善良、良好嘅公民質素。<br />\n呢個selling point係拎到好多同情分，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家要記得我地簽美國聯署、登報果d舉動就係想外國介入啊！</span><br />\n再識玩D，直頭喊晒同旅客講：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「我地無得揀先揀機場集會，唔係想阻你地，而係得機場先唔會比警察開槍掃射！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 外國鏡頭前，顧一下形象</span></strong><br />\n捉公安當然無問題啦，大大力證明政府同狗講大話添！不過外國鏡頭影住下，要顧下形象啊！<br />\n你地咁多人已經圍住左佢，佢都走唔到，袋又搜緊喇，其實可以請佢飲啖茶食個包，一邊慢慢問架。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">再幽默D咪帶佢去食返碗叉燒飯，一盡香港人好客之道囉，比人睇下我地連對戰俘都好好禮數嘛。</span><br />\n咁樣講唔係忘記同公安嘅不共戴天之仇，<strong>而係鏡頭前嘅策略。</strong><br />\n如果無外國鏡頭，我話知你地私刑打到佢仆街啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地而家企出嚟就係爭取自由民主人權丫嘛，係外國好睇重嘅野，所以唔能夠自相矛盾呀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結！機場集會其實真係無得輸，大家都見到今日D白衫狗好緊張D小狗有無自己衝入去或者有無上齊車。即係佢地都知機場入面唔可以有警暴畫面，唔能夠武力清場，<strong>即係我地做對了。</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要做嘅野就係比旅客睇到我地幾咁慘幾咁和平，對比返黑警殘暴不仁。<br />\n至於搞到機場D機飛唔到，嗱，係政府話要停，我地都唔知點解架～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我地一定會當你屋企人一樣，你想去邊我地教你，你無野食我地會分比你。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為呢個就係真．香港人嘅公民質素！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c13216fdf6ccbb13150ffb9de11c32f713a778bc","tid":1468516,"uid":252934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"78cd7c9201dc6d269069f17d2b575b14ee7c42fe","tid":1468516,"uid":11515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:03:05.000Z","msg":"《香港機場說明書》全部同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"622babbcd0723153ebd05aee7366b0454633376d","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:35.000Z","msg":"自推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbdc051c905b99dfd211c3dce0d70bf7e28963a","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:05:22.000Z","msg":"3點幾都寫咁長，比個面推下啦～"},{"pid":"27a932053e1bdd9514299637f1446d2339e72146","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:51.000Z","msg":"呢個係重點啊：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「我地無得揀先揀機場集會，唔係想阻你地，而係得機場先唔會比警察開槍掃射！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」</span>"},{"pid":"cd7c1f85916134a26bcf6228bc718eea02f5b985","tid":1468516,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247135e1bf45af54dd0015b79999ffacbd19920f","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:09:42.000Z","msg":"又要自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99131d0f028c3e36aa5249e06556af2f63a8efae","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:11:42.000Z","msg":"要識打國際輿論戰啊<br />\n可能係致勝關鍵"},{"pid":"6819c30283d6ddedc061517dc7b7e6f5c8ee4bbc","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:12:41.000Z","msg":"同埋女急救員爆眼，我地真係好傷心好傷心好心痛<br />\n唔需要忍住眼淚架<br />\n就同外國旅客盡情表達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff823094d1ce11d245ed149c53749335b8e62520","tid":1468516,"uid":296055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:17:53.000Z","msg":"各位請幫忙分享出去！！！如果你們願意，請幫忙分享以下道歉文章到自己的Facebook,ig,爭取在林鄭講廢話指責我地之前，為811及812中在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉而道歉。並請繼續分享出去！！！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n鑒於這兩天於機場舉行的和平理性機場集會，為各位旅客帶不便，在此，我們真心誠意向各位致歉。<br />\n<br />\nWe would like to sincerely apologize for all the inconvenience caused by the peaceful demonstration at the HK International Airport over the last two days.<br />\n<br />\n我們重申，今次的機場集會，目的為和平理性地引起政府回應及國際關注，希望各位能夠體諒，香港人爭取五大訴求嘅初衷。<br />\n<br />\nOur demonstration aims to peacefully raise the awareness of the global community, as well as response from the HK government on the five demands from the public of Hong Kong. We thank you for your tolerance and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n我們再次向在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉，感謝各位的諒解。<br />\n<br />\nTo all the reporters, ambulance staff, airport staff and affected passengers, we again would like to express oir deepest apology to all the inconvenience and disruptions<br />\n<br />\n感謝所有仍堅持初心嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n一群等待政府回應訴求的香港人"},{"pid":"3fb9e1690f184b3816c237d07ce034c8a617bdbd","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:26:47.000Z","msg":"睡前一推"},{"pid":"9a3318362d10e73e7d3d23271a137fb16b488a14","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:37:31.000Z","msg":"再輕輕一推"},{"pid":"920c70b980283d0efcce96ddeeca2f3019c4ea8c","tid":1468516,"uid":277750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:12:49.000Z","msg":"👍"},{"pid":"969e2df4bdff6d028deac55c0de30e06d76515ad","tid":1468516,"uid":266491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T22:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19ce423e9f969e8fb3d3356574a95368b028cdf","tid":1468516,"uid":245473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:35:50.000Z","msg":"推，每次修正係重點。我地一定要贏！"},{"pid":"abc5a4d7785aaadd264e4894db54472e5110eb4f","tid":1468516,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45502b3d90155c56b49f664aa2ea56876d857d4","tid":1468516,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:45:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"951101e98b782829e764b57404664d44a5da3aec","tid":1468516,"uid":258421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:55:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e16ba0461ee58fe269fe941680dc062dda33887c","tid":1468516,"uid":258421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:55:12.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5ab3de6b991afb1fd57bad5039e110873a6d961c","tid":1468516,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0c4767cbe86a89265c765f37079fd45f08762b2","tid":1468516,"uid":282947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:11:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0625dd42240131d205b038727fa6cba5d0cf04d6","tid":1468516,"uid":266491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}